# ============================================================
#  .gitignore for kiande.com — 30 Days of Dahl
# ============================================================
#
#  IMPORTANT — this project differs from the Eleventy boilerplate:
#  _site/ is NOT generated output here. There is no build step;
#  _site/ is the hand-authored web root (Laragon vhost points at it)
#  and MUST stay in git. Do not add _site/ to this file.
# ============================================================

# --- Scratch / working folders (Daniel's conventions) ---
_temp/
_md/TESTING.md

# --- Node (only ever used for one-off asset tooling, never runtime) ---
node_modules/

# --- OS junk ---
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

# --- Editor files ---
*.swp
*.swo
.idea/
.vscode/
